The capital city is Kuressaare. The county is Saaremaa, the largest island of Estonia, and several smaller islands near it. Notable islands are Muhu, Ruhnu, Abruka and Vilsandi. == Municipalities == The county is divided into municipalities. There are 3 rural municipalities in Saare County.
